{"tid":338383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中印角力】護照印「CHINA」禁足邊界重地？ 台2大學生遭喀什米爾拒入境","createTime":"2017-07-28T07:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T05:15:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc79783cda272376f017e9f19c91296c4c0b3464","tid":338383,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170728/large/1501207784_3105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170728%2Flarge%2F1501207784_3105.jpg&h=b06f6ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中印邊界問題爭議持續發酵，雙方處於正處於軍事對峙狀態，竟連累到台灣旅客。2名台灣大學生赴印度旅遊，昨天在靠近喀什米爾的喜馬偕爾省首府西姆拉（Shimla）申請進入許可證時，因護照上有「CHINA」而被拒入境。<br />\n<br />\n中印部隊近期在邊境對峙超過一個月，雙方敵意升溫。2名台灣大學生昨日（27日）在西姆拉申請進入許可證時，遭當地基層官員以護照上有「CHINA」為由，拒絕發出進入許可證。兩名大學生求助台灣駐印度代表處，代表處人員向當地負責核發許可證的官員解釋，台灣與中國的不同，但因基層官員不敢負責，電話不斷轉給上級，官員才同意核發。<br />\n其實，印度大部份官員，尤其是關卡和海關官員，對台灣與中國大陸分治不是很清楚，包括喀什米爾、東北七省、靠近中印邊境敏感地區等，台灣民眾經常被誤認為來自中國，遭拒絕核發進入許可。<br />\n台灣駐印度代表處官員向當地官員解釋，同時傳真資料到印度內政部，有關兩岸民眾分別將文件交給對方核對，終於讓當地官員了解相關規定，同意核發進入許可證給兩名台灣的大學生。駐印度代表處多次向印度政府反映後，印度內政部已向各地，尤其是敏感地區設立的關卡和海關核發通知，說明台灣旅客不在限制進入喀什米爾、東北七省等敏感地區的範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170728/57011297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170728%2F57011297&d=xBlQXd77gvrjpVxQ%2FSq06p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b9db0122\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170728%2F57011297&h=b44ab7e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170728/57011297</a><br />\n<br />\n一早講咗台灣人都係支那人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74976eac9432822495270072e85b58237825c951","tid":338383,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"一早講咗台灣人都係支那人架啦,明明大家語言一樣都係蝗語,一樣同支那人一樣咁無恥,仲有黑心食物,坑溝油,佢哋最無資格話香港人係中國人,但班垃圾台狗又堅持自己唔係,明明大大個支那民國喺度"},{"pid":"4d1ea37d83c6cb026113660e9fb1d55f3a5c1695","tid":338383,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"再堅持中華民國嗰啲一定係鬼"},{"pid":"92d88d4bdb9045e3239ee9e45a40a82bba5c4221","tid":338383,"uid":63154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:10:30.000Z","msg":"........其實，印度大部份官員，尤其是關卡和海關官員，對台灣與中國大陸分治不是很清楚......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢句再次曝露蘋果最底嗰浸思想，用中國大陸分治去形容台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb7b79d3a074a2a829111217272f4777b56d527","tid":338383,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a509a5dca7c3f69e873b33e7a25414fb83f769e","tid":338383,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>........其實，印度大部份官員，尤其是關卡和海關官員，對台灣與中國大陸分治不是很清楚......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢句再次曝露蘋果最底嗰浸思想，用中國大陸分治去形容台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係今日先知肥佬係大中華膠"},{"pid":"bd36296b7779bc76c58b690aeb3cca9a094abef2","tid":338383,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20120530/large/30fx31pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20120530%2Flarge%2F30fx31pzok.jpg&h=f9e4ad4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gsaj.gov.mo/sites/www.gsaj.gov.mo/files/FOTO%201_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gsaj.gov.mo%2Fsites%2Fwww.gsaj.gov.mo%2Ffiles%2FFOTO%25201_0.jpg&h=b9c1ce3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSd0ZMI4i_mrLr-r4CE1iMGt0Y8iAadIWT_iJdP3qbLoyWSAB3T\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSd0ZMI4i_mrLr-r4CE1iMGt0Y8iAadIWT_iJdP3qbLoyWSAB3T&h=1aa1ef50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟呢3本一樣 有CHINA字"},{"pid":"b61800dbe4bd4055dfe24abd3e441da8b6aaebb7","tid":338383,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2486e52b583a336ab7d9d19a0e58d40b6c29daf6","tid":338383,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e069a1c303708f54d7d62f12b05a0b1836e874ce","tid":338383,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"拎得China個名就食得鹹魚抵得渴啦"},{"pid":"e232cf78842465f1bb70a47b57729e01549a6c3a","tid":338383,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>........其實，印度大部份官員，尤其是關卡和海關官員，對台灣與中國大陸分治不是很清楚......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢句再次曝露蘋果最底嗰浸思想，用中國大陸分治去形容台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒蘋不嬲大中華膠嚟"},{"pid":"12634ee471588bfa7c2449369273e2a256e02257","tid":338383,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"快撚d改名割蓆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518b391699e853715987a2d23948659fd862a0d4","tid":338383,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:23:56.000Z","msg":"BNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"